# Copied to `.env.development` / `.env.production` as needed (Vite loads `.env*` automatically).

# `pnpm dev`: proxy `/api` → this origin. Default in vite.config.ts is http://127.0.0.1:8080 (WeKnora / Vue frontend 常用端口).
# VITE_DEV_BACKEND=http://127.0.0.1:8080

# `pnpm build`: browser calls API at this origin (empty = same host; usually set for production).
# VITE_BACKEND_ORIGIN=https://your-weknora-host
